        super.print(document);
    }
}
```
This refactoring separates the responsibilities of printing from scanning and faxing, adhering to the Single Responsibility Principle (SRP). The BasicPrinter class is now responsible for printing only, while AdvancedPrinter extends it and inherits its print functionality.

**OCP**
